        <h4>This is a very easy raw milk ice cream recipe</h4>
        <h5>Ingredients</h5>
        <ul>
            <li>4 cups Raw Milk poured out from the Galllon jar</li>
            <li>3/4 cuo sugar or Maple syrup</li>
            <li>1 Tablespoon vanilla</li>
        </ul>
        <h5>Steps</h5>
        <ol>
            <li>Pour 4 cups of raw milk without stirring it first into a measuring cup</li>
            <li>Whisk in sugar/Maple syrup unit dissolved</li>
            <li>immediatelay pour into your ice cream maker (if your freezer bowl sets out for more then 15 minutes re chill)</li>
            <li>Churn your ice cream</li>
            <li>Once your ice cream is done immediately eat or freeze unti ready</li>
        </ol>
        <h5>Note</h5>
        <p>The sugar is what prevents ice crystals from forming</p>
        
